sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as User
  participant UI as Next.js UI (CBTLogForm)
  participant H as useCBTAnalysis()
  participant API as FastAPI /api/v1/cbt-logs/analyze
  participant A as AIClient (model-agnostic)
  participant M as Model provider (Gemini / other)

  U->>UI: Enter situation + automatic thoughts
  UI->>H: analyze(situation, automaticThought)\n(mandatory for CBT flow)
  H->>API: POST /api/v1/cbt-logs/analyze
  API->>A: get_ai_client().analyze_cbt()
  A->>M: Generate structured suggestions + reframes
  M-->>A: JSON response
  API-->>H: CBTAnalysisResponse
  H-->>UI: analysis state updated
  UI-->>U: Show suggestions + reframes (HITL selection)
